---
import SocialLinks from "../core/SocialLinks.astro";
---

<section
  class="relative top-80 lg:top-36 md:top-64 w-full min-h-screen flex items-center flex-col justify-start pb-10"
>
  <div
    class="w-[50vw] h-[2px] animate-border bg-[length:400%_400%] rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-blue to-red-600"
  >
  </div>
  <h1
    class="w-2/3 text-3xl md:text-xl sm:text-sm font-normal font-clash text-left md:text-center dark:text-white-60 text-black-60 mt-32 md:mt-28 sm:mt-20"
    data-aos="flip-up"
    data-aos-delay="300"
    data-aos-duration="1000"
  >
    Are you a business owner trying to establish internet presence?
  </h1>
  <h4
    class="w-2/3 text-lg md:text-md sm:text-sm font-bold font-ranade text-left md:text-center dark:text-white-80 mt-10 md:mt-8 sm:mt-6"
    data-aos="flip-down"
    data-aos-delay="600"
    data-aos-duration="1000"
  >
    I can help you build your brand and create a space for your business in this
    vast world of internet with absolute ease.
  </h4>
  <div
    class="w-[50vw] h-[2px] animate-border bg-[length:400%_400%] rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-blue to-red-600 mt-32"
  >
  </div>
  <h1
    class="w-2/3 text-3xl md:text-xl sm:text-sm font-normal font-clash text-left md:text-center dark:text-white-60 text-black-60 mt-32 md:mt-28 sm:mt-20"
    data-aos="flip-up"
    data-aos-delay="300"
    data-aos-duration="1000"
  >
    Maybe you already have your business running in the internet, But is it
    hidden? Do you want to polish and build reach?
  </h1>
  <h4
    class="w-2/3 text-lg md:text-md sm:text-sm font-bold font-ranade text-left md:text-center dark:text-white-80 mt-10 md:mt-8 sm:mt-6"
    data-aos="flip-down"
    data-aos-delay="600"
    data-aos-duration="1000"
  >
    I can help you polish your brand and create a reach for your business
    seamlessly.
  </h4>
  <div
    class="w-[50vw] h-[2px] animate-border bg-[length:400%_400%] rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-blue to-red-600 mt-32"
  >
  </div>
  <div
    class="flex flex-row sm:flex-col justify-center items-center gap-6 mt-10 md:mt-8 sm:mt-6"
  >
    <h2
      class="sm:w-2/3 md:w-1/3 text-lg md:text-md sm:text-sm font-ranade text-center dark:text-white-80"
      data-aos-anchor-placement="top-bottom"
      data-aos="zoom-out-right"
      data-aos-delay="600"
      data-aos-duration="1000"
    >
      Just drop an email or connect to get started.
    </h2>
    <SocialLinks pageType="footer" />
  </div>
</section>
